    I(P_4, x) = (1+3x) × Q(x)
  I(P_ 5, x) = 1 + 5x + 6x^2 + x^3
    at x=2: 43, at x=-1/3: -0.037037
  I(P_ 6, x) = 1 + 6x + 10x^2 + 4x^3
