  I(P_8, 2) =    341  vs  (2^9+(-1)^n)/3 = 171
  I(P_9, 2) =    683  vs  (2^10+(-1)^n)/3 = 341

CORRECTED: I(P_n, 2) = (2^{n+1} + (-1)^n)/3

  I(P_0, 2) = (2 + 1)/3 = 1 ✓
  I(P_1, 2) = (4 - 1)/3 = 1 ✗ (should be 3)

